Antipattern Detected: Functional Decomposition: Using the include relationship

   Instance 1: Constructs Involved: Create Listing, Upload Photos, include (Create Listing → Upload Photos)
   Instance 1: Explanation: "Upload Photos" is an inclusion use case included only by "Create Listing". It is not associated with any actor directly, is not included by any other use case, does not include or extend any other use case, and is not extended by or generalized with any use case. This represents functional decomposition where the act of uploading photos — a sub-step of creating a listing — has been improperly separated into its own use case that provides no standalone observable result to any actor.

